
Select all elements with an attribute value that ends with specific characters
[attribute$="value"]


Example --->>>> Select the items for names that end with 'ato'

              <div class="table">
              <apple class="small" />
              <bento for="Hayato">
              <pickle />
              </bento>
              <apple for="Ryota" />
              <plate for="Minato">
              <orange />
              </plate>
              <pickle class="small" />
              </div>

ans --->>> bento[for],plate[for]
